The '''Luminous Gardens''' was a health [[Spa/Legends|spa]] on a hill above the [[Boiling Sea]] of [[Drall (planet)|Drall]].  It was operated by [[Drusa]], a young female [[Drall/Legends|Drall]].  The spa featured hot spring and mineral baths, mud soaks, aromatherapy, and masseuses.<ref>[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]</ref> The [[Fountain]] was a restaurant located in the spa. [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] met there to discuss [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]].<ref name="LOTF">''[[Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice]]''</ref>

